			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-640244">
									

<p>507 is the shifter.</p>
<p>What's the difficulty: Two 507s shift in from other realities as our 507 shifts out. Turns out 507 and the smiling man have a deeper connection than we may have expected. Oh, and the foundation is just a TEENY bit evil. :p</p>
<p>I would expect the remaining 507 to have tried to buy time by telling them about other SCP encounters in his homeworld, but I guess with the fact he has internet access it's likely he doesn't know too much about other SCPs.</p>

