					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ksaid" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1484103); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1484103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610164509" alt="ksaid" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1484103)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ksaid" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1484103); return false;" >ksaid</a></span> <span class="odate time_1356776745 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">29 Dec 2012 10:25</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1673093">
									

<p>Could you imagine how awkward that conversation would be?</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">I&nbsp;can.</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><em>SCP-507:</em> You <em>dissected</em> him?</p>
<p><em>DR X:</em> Indeed. it was very educational. For the record, we found a tumour in his left leg, you might want to get that looked at.</p>
<p><em>SCP-507:</em> How did you know he wasn't <em>me</em>?</p>
<p><em>DR X:</em> Simple. He thought General Lee killed Lincoln.</p>
<p><em>SCP-507:</em> Didn't he?</p>
<p>(There is roughly five seconds of silence.)</p>
<p><em>DR X:</em> &#8230; seriously?</p>
<p><em>SCP-507:</em> [EXPLETIVE REDACTED]! [EXPLETIVE REDACTED]! Seriously!</p>
<p><em>DR X:</em> How could you not know Booth killed Lincoln! <em>Didn't you go to school?</em></p>
<p><em>SCP-507:</em> Yeah! <em>For two week intervals at the ████ ██ Asylum!</em></p>
<p><em>DR X:</em> I think we might need a password.</p>
<p><em>SCP-507:</em> I think you might need to <em>stop dissecting me!</em></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Ah, sitcom style witty banter. The lowest form of comedy.</p>

							</div>

								
					
